title: Metalliska - A Ska Tribute to 80's Metal
description:
A compilation of the throat-bustin' vocals and melodramatic guitar riffs of 80's metal and the thrashing fun of ska/punk and you can only expect..wild and eccentric misfits with a heck of a lot of fun in store for you. Reel Big Fish, Less Than Jake & more!
